trans-unit.source: Creates the theme-specific look for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet*> elements. A <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet*> defines the appearance of <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.RadioButton"></xref> elements.
trans-unit.target: Cria o aspeto de tema específicos para [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-wpf-md.md)] <> </> *> elementos. A <> </> *> define o aspecto do <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.CheckBox"> </xref> e <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.RadioButton"> </xref> elementos.

trans-unit.source: The actual appearance of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet%2A> is dependent on which theme is active on the user's system.
trans-unit.target: O aspeto real do <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet%2A>depende de qual tema está ativo no sistema do utilizador.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.BulletDecorator.Bullet%2A>

trans-unit.source: The properties of this class allow [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to set the appearance based on the current theme.
trans-unit.target: As propriedades desta classe permitem [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para definir o aspecto com base no tema actual.

trans-unit.source: In XAML usage, a BulletChrome object element can also have child content, which can be a single <xref:System.Windows.UIElement> that sets the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Na utilização XAML, um elemento de objecto BulletChrome também pode ter conteúdo subordinado, o que pode ser um único <xref:System.Windows.UIElement>que define o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Decorator.Child%2A> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement>
